Notes:
- remap Caps_Lock to Escape:
    sudo vim /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/pc

- reload terminal configuration:
    dconf load /org/gnome/terminal/legacy/profiles:/ < gnome-terminal-profiles.dconf
